    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2777325248" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2777325248" />
    <a title="Paltia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7271273-paltia"><img alt="Paltia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1545851814p2/7271273.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2777325248?book_show_action=true">Apr 08, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Paltia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Paltia" href="/user/show/7271273-paltia">Paltia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2777325248" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16577144974081867386">Five stars for the nearly non stop laugh out loud moments. Juice Terry, the mischievous one, spreading confusion, delusion and sheer delight as he drives on by in his cab. He takes what he wants behaving as if he’s out for himself. A man who seems to know who he is - the one who whispers rash ideas in your ears and carefree thoughts into your head at bedtime. He can be found around those who are lost and filled with doubt. He’ll bring out your wild side with his reckless style all for the sheer </span>
  <span id="freeText16577144974081867386" style="display:none">Five stars for the nearly non stop laugh out loud moments. Juice Terry, the mischievous one, spreading confusion, delusion and sheer delight as he drives on by in his cab. He takes what he wants behaving as if he’s out for himself. A man who seems to know who he is - the one who whispers rash ideas in your ears and carefree thoughts into your head at bedtime. He can be found around those who are lost and filled with doubt. He’ll bring out your wild side with his reckless style all for the sheer thrills. Crafty and cunning he delights in provoking others to audacious thoughts inviting them to try new ways to manage responsibilities. He does what he does well and beneath all that bravado is a proverbial heart of gold. Jings! Barry! Aye sur, aye sur. What a ride.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16577144974081867386" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

